[Student "S"]
{NORTH's positive response shows 8+ points and five or more cards headed by at least two honors.

SOUTH figures a small slam would be safe, but just to be sure she uses Blackwood.

NORTH's 6\D reply shows one Key-card which must be the trump King, 
and a \D void!.

SOUTH readjusts her thinking and decides to bid the Grand.}

